Paper: hep-th/9511112

Date: 1995-11-15

Title: Supersymmetry and localization

Authors: Albert Schwarz and Oleg Zaboronsky

Comments: 16 pages, LATEX

Journal-ref: Commun.Math.Phys. 183 (1997) 463-476

We study conditions under which an odd symmetry of the integrand leads tolocalization of the corresponding integral over a (super)manifold. We also showthat in many cases these conditions guarantee exactness of the stationary phaseapproximation of such integrals.